title: The Badass Root | Person Of Interest
author: Ashely Corner
comment: Root has to be the best characters to come out of a TV series and no one could  be Root but Amy Acker.
Her smile is so devious it makes her gorgeous.
Flat out best lesbian character of all time. Plus Amy Ackers face is so perfect
i don't even know what to do with my life anymore. after watching that, i just dedicated more of my life to her. I'm done.
Why do they always kill the good characters???????
